text: Leyton Orient Women F.C. is a women's football team based in Leyton, London in England. The team compete in the FA Women's National League Division One South East. The club play home games at Mile End Stadium. Leyton Orient Women are nicknamed The O's, and their supporters maintain rivalries with Crawley Wasps. ==References== Category:Women's football clubs in England
